<html>
<head>
	<script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-latest.min.js" type="text/javascript" href="quiz.js"></script>
	<script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.10.2/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css">

</head>

<body>
	<center>
		<h1>Uncomfort Yourself</h1>

		<%= form_for @result do |f| %>
		<%= f.hidden_field :score %>
		<%= f.hidden_field :emotional_result %>
		<%= f.hidden_field :physical_result %>

		<div class="question emotional">
			<img src="/atparty.jpg" class="medium"> </br>
			1. You're showing up at a party alone. How do you feel? <br>

			<input class ="answers" type="radio" name="q1" value="2" id="q1a"/><label for="q1a">Very Bothered</label><br/>     
			<input class ="answers" type="radio" name="q1" value="1" id="q1b"/><label for="q1b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/> 
			<input class ="answers" type="radio" name="q1" value="0" id="q1c"/><label for="q1c">Not Bothered</label><br/>       
		</div>




		<div class="question physical">
			<img src="https://encrypted-tbn1.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSjxl8tJZe9J09Lnff0BZ4rsy5m0UJs2mRRG774YN-R3EIk9660" class="medium"><br>
			2. You encounter one of these creatures. What's your reaction? <br>       

			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q2" value="2" id="q2a"/><label for="q2a">Very Bothered</label><br/>      
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q2" value="1" id="q2b"/><label for="q2b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>   
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q2" value="0" id="q2c"/><label for="q2c">Not Bothered</label><br/>        
		</div>


		<div class="question physical">
			<img src="/cliff-walking.jpg" class="medium"><br>
			3. You're hiking along a cliff's edge. How's it going?<br>        

			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q3" value="2" id="q3a"/><label for="q3a">Very Bothered</label><br/>        
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q3" value="1" id="q3b"/><label for="q3b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>    
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q3" value="0" id="q3c"/><label for="q3c">Not Bothered</label><br/>        
		</div>

		<div class="question emotional">
			<img src="/teen-with-hands-on-head.jpg" class="medium"><br>
			4. Think about something you're struggling with. How do you feel about asking for help?<br>        

			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q4" value="2" id="q4a"/><label for="q4a">Very Bothered</label><br/>        
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q4" value="1" id="q4b"/><label for="q4b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>   
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q4" value="0" id="q4c"/><label for="q4c">Not Bothered</label><br/>        
		</div>       

		<div class="question">
			<img src="/Stuck-in-Elevator.jpg" class="medium"><br>
			5. What if you're trapped in an elevator for an hour?<br>        
			
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q5" value="2" id="q5a"/><label for="q5a">Very Bothered</label><br/>        
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q5" value="1" id="q5b"/><label for="q5b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>    
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q5" value="0" id="q5c"/><label for="q5c">Not Bothered</label><br/>         
		</div>        

		<div class="question physical">
			<img src="/pitbull.jpg" class="medium"><br>
			6. You run into a dog at the park, or on the sidewalk. How do you feel?<br>        
			
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q6" value="2" id="q6a"/><label for="q6a">Very Bothered</label><br/>        
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q6" value="1" id="q6b"/><label for="q6b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>    
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q6" value="0" id="q6c"/><label for="q6c">Not Bothered</label><br/>        
		</div>       

		<div class="question emotional">
			<img src="/busy-at-work-or-productive.jpg" class="medium"><br>
			7. You've been assigned to a new project at work and it involves many things you don't know right now. How does that make you feel?<br>        

			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q7" value="2" id="q7a"/><label for="q7a">Very Bothered</label><br/>       
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q7" value="1" id="q7b"/><label for="q7b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>    
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q7" value="0" id="q7c"/><label for="q7c">Not Bothered</label><br/>        
		</div>       

		<div class="question emotional">
			<img src="/shopping-mall2.jpg" class="medium"><br>
			8. You've got errands to run today, at a busy, crowded shopping centre. How are you feeling?<br>        

			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q8" value="2" id="q8a"/><label for="q8a">Very Bothered</label><br/>        
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q8" value="1" id="q8b"/><label for="q8b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>    
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q8" value="0" id="q8c"/><label for="q8c">Not Bothered</label><br/>         
		</div>       

		<div class="question emotional">
			<img src="/speech.jpeg" class="medium"><br>
			9. You've got to give a speech in front of a large crowd.<br>        

			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q9" value="2" id="q9a"/><label for="q9a">Very Bothered</label><br/>          
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q9" value="1" id="q9b"/><label for="q9b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>     
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q9" value="0" id="q9c"/><label for="q9c">Not Bothered</label><br/>            
		</div>       

		<div class="question physical">
			<img src="/cn_image.size.plane-taking-off-storm.jpg" class="medium"><br>
			10. You're on an airplane. It's stormy outside, but the flight has been cleared for takeoff. How will you feel during the flight?<br>       
			
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q10" value="2" id="q10a"/><label for="q10a">Very Bothered</label><br/>       
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q10" value="1" id="q10b"/><label for="q10b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>  
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q10" value="0" id="q10c"/><label for="q10c">Not Bothered</label><br/>         
		</div>       

		<div class="question physical">
			<img src="/dr-t.jpeg" class="medium"><br>
			11. Time for your yearly checkup. How do feel?<br>

			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q11" value="2" id="q11a"/><label for="q11a">Very Bothered</label><br/>      
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q11" value="1" id="q11b"/><label for="q11b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>   
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q11" value="0" id="q11c"/><label for="q11c">Not Bothered</label><br/>          
		</div>

		<div class="question physical">
			<img src="/handwashing.jpg" class="medium"><br>
			12. You've touched many hand railings, buttons and door handles today, but haven't had a chance to wash your hands. How's your mood?<br>
			
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q12" value="2" id="q12a"/><label for="q12a">Very Bothered</label><br/>       
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q12" value="1" id="q12b"/><label for="q12b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>   
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q12" value="0" id="q12c"/><label for="q12c">Not Bothered</label><br/>           
		</div> 
 
		<div class="question emotional">
			<img src="/power-out.jpg" class="medium"><br>
			13. There's a power outage and you're home alone. How would you react?<br>
			
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q13" value="2" id="q13a"/><label for="q13a">Very Bothered</label><br/>       
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q13" value="1" id="q13b"/><label for="q13b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>   
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q13" value="0" id="q13c"/><label for="q13c">Not Bothered</label><br/>         
		</div>	

		<div class="question emotional">
			<img src="/study-stuff.jpg" class="medium"><br>
			14. You're preparing for a test or exam. How do you feel on the night before?<br>
			
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q14" value="2" id="q14a"/><label for="q14a">Very Bothered</label><br/>       
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q14" value="1" id="q14b"/><label for="q14b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>   
			<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q14" value="0" id="q14c"/><label for="q14c">Not Bothered</label><br/>          
		</div>   

		<div class="question physical">
			<div class="last">
				<img src="/strange-menu-hanoi-vietnam.jpg" class="medium"><br>
				15. You're travelling in a foreign country and you need to eat but you don't recognize anything on the menu. What's your reaction?<br>

				<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q15" value="2" id="q15a"/><label for="q15a">Very Bothered</label><br/> 
				<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q15" value="1" id="q15b"/><label for="q15b">Slightly Bothered</label><br/>
				<input class="answers" type="radio" name="q15" value="0" id="q15c"/><label for="q15c">Not Bothered</label><br/>      
			</div>
		</div> 
		<br/>

		<div id="results">
			
			<%= f.submit "Show me my Results!" %> <br>
			<img src="/finished.png"> <br>      
		</div>

		<input type="button" id='next' value= 'next' />


		<% end %>

	</center>
</body>			
</html>